    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-5 col-12">
            <h4 class="mt-4">ASP.NET (MVC) Demos</h4>
            <ul class="list-group shadow mb-5">
                <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-light">
                    <a href="https://addressbook.kgivler.com" class="alist" target="_blank">Address Book MVC</a> - ASP.NET MVC: Address Book Demo.
