                <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-light">
                    <a href="https://fizzbuzz.kgivler.com" class="alist" target="_blank">Fizz Buzz MVC</a> - ASP.NET MVC: Classic Fizz Buzz challenge.
                </li>
                <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-dark">
                    <a href="https://rotator.kgivler.com" class="alist" target="_blank">Rotator MVC</a> - ASP.NET MVC: Palindrome detector.
                </li>
            </ul>

            <h4 class="mt-4">Frontend Demos</h4>
            <ul class="list-group shadow mb-5">
                <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-light">
                    <a href="~/LoanShark/" class="alist" target="_blank">Loan Shark</a>
