                    <a href="~/REwind/index.html" class="alist" target="_blank">REwind</a> - JavaScript coding challenge: Reverse a string.
                </li>
                <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-light">
                    <a href="~/Hundo/index.html" class="alist" target="_blank">Hundo</a> - JavaScript coding challenge: Display even numbers in bold.
                </li>
