            <h4 class="mt-4">Bootstrap Layout Examples</h4>
            <ul class="list-group shadow mb-5">
                <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-light">
                    Bootstrap Grids: 
                    <a href="~/demos/BootstrapAndTheGrids/index.html" class="alist" target="_blank"> Demo Grid Layouts</a>
